Contains the hip height of the [Humanoid](https://create.roblox.com/docs/reference/engine/classes/Humanoid) of the model that was used to
author this [KeyframeSequence](https://create.roblox.com/docs/reference/engine/classes/KeyframeSequence). Default value is 1.35 since that is the
hip height set for a standard R15 [character](https://create.roblox.com/docs/reference/engine/classes/Character).
